125
00:16:15,243 --> 00:16:17,243
You miss me, kid?

126
00:16:17,243 --> 00:16:18,583
Not really.

127
00:16:18,683 --> 00:16:21,063
How are you doing?
- I'm OK. How are you?

128
00:16:21,571 --> 00:16:23,551
Who's this?
- This is Bobby. He's my...

129
00:16:23,651 --> 00:16:25,391
