136
00:16:44,251 --> 00:16:47,129
We need a baby-sitter.
- Baby-sitter?

137
00:16:48,405 --> 00:16:50,435
Nice to see you again, Logan.

138
00:16:50,725 --> 00:16:52,725
Hi, Logan.

139
00:16:53,525 --> 00:16:55,145
Hi, Jean.

140
00:16:55,245 --> 00:16:57,918
