208
00:27:47,619 --> 00:27:50,349
You have him?
- He's not going anywhere.

209
00:27:50,379 --> 00:27:52,609
Are you?

210
00:27:52,739 --> 00:27:55,399
Please don't kill me.
I didn't mean to harm anyone.

211
00:27:55,499 --> 00:27:58,650
