221
00:28:43,441 --> 00:28:47,431
I'd rather get him back to the professor.
- The professor?

222
00:28:53,266 --> 00:28:57,496
- Did you do these yourself?
- Yes.

223
00:29:03,426 --> 00:29:05,426
